item.title: CVE-2017-5688|2024-08-05T15:11:47.387Z -- intel%20corporation -- solid%20state%20drive%20toolbox
item.description: There is an escalation of privilege vulnerability in the Intel Solid State Drive Toolbox versions before 3.4.5 which allow a local administrative attacker to load and execute arbitrary code.
